nodes.text: Star Wars Insider 163 is the 141st issue of Star Wars Insider magazine and the seventy-first published by Titan Magazines. It was released on February 2, 2016.

The Force has awoken! As Star Wars: The Force Awakens breaks box office records, Insider looks behind the scenes as the cast and crew discuss the film. Plus: take an in-depth look at Star Wars Rebels on TV, we delve again into the Jedi Toy Box, present a must-read story, and a look at the latest books, comics, and collectibles!
